      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>67</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282319</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>この空間には『UNKNOWN』で
強者と戦った場合のみ、
開く扉がある……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In this distortion, there is a door that opens only when
you fight a powerful opponent on “UNKNOWN."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>68</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282392</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>おまえたちに、
その扉を開く力はあるか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you have the strenght to open that door...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>69</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
